Libertad Sublime HD Hack Cheats

Libertad Sublime HD Hack Cheats can be used for iOS and Android, and there is no need Jailbreak or root. Tested on multiple device works perfectly, and is updated automatically. Below are instructions for using this cheat

Instructions:
